&lt;p&gt;I also discovered that &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3342&quot; title=&quot;Allow conditions in case statement&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-3342&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-3342&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; didn&apos;t update AliasMasker.g and included the change in the new patch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
